author: Joe Sheppard For Mailonline
title: London Fashion Week features crazy intergalactic costumes | Daily Mail Online
text: show ad It's what we'll all be wearing next season: Pink beards, pointed helmets and massive orange tentacles are among the bizarre looks out on the catwalk at London Fashion Week The futuristic met the bizarre at the On|Off event at the Oxo Tower in the capital on Friday The clothes were created by London-based designer Jack Irving, who has previously worked with Lady Gaga He says his vision is to create a 'cosmic world for alien showgirls to parade through'
